WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.450 --> 00:00:01.640
Awesome work.

00:00:01.640 --> 00:00:04.650
You've added the core platforming
mechanic to Gigagal and

00:00:04.650 --> 00:00:06.890
worked out some sophisticated
game logic to do so.

00:00:07.900 --> 00:00:11.720
I hope you're already starting to get
some fun ideas for level designs.

00:00:11.720 --> 00:00:12.410
Right now though,

00:00:12.410 --> 00:00:15.790
you only have one screen's worth
of platforms to work with.

00:00:15.790 --> 00:00:17.250
In the next level, let's fix that,

00:00:17.250 --> 00:00:20.220
by allowing the camera to
follow Gigagal around.

00:00:20.220 --> 00:00:20.720
See you there.

